#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid ""
"Checking the ext2 (revision 0) file system in partition #${PARTITION} of "
"${DEVICE}..."
msgstr ""
"Yn gwirio'r system ffeiliau ext2 (diwygiad 0) yn y rhaniad #${PARTITION} ar "
"${DEVICE}..."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid "Go back to the menu and correct errors?"
msgstr "Mynd yn ôl i'r ddewislen a chywiro gwallau?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid ""
"The test of the file system with type ext2 (revision 0) in partition #"
"${PARTITION} of ${DEVICE} found uncorrected errors."
msgstr ""
"Canfuodd brawf y system ffeilau gyda'r math ext2 (diwygiad 0) yn rhaniad #"
"${PARTITION} ar ${DEVICE} wallau heb eu cywiro."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid ""
"If you do not go back to the partitioning menu and correct these errors, the "
"partition will not be used at all."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych chi'n mynd yn ôl i'r ddewislen rhaniadu a chywiro'r gwallau "
"hyn, ni chaiff y rhaniad ei ddefnyddio o gwbl."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:16
msgid "Failed to create a file system"
msgstr "Methwyd creu system ffeiliau"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:16
msgid ""
"The ext2 (revision 0) file system creation in partition #${PARTITION} of "
"${DEVICE} failed."
msgstr ""
"Methwyd creu system ffeiliau ext2 (diwygiad 0) yn rhaniad #${PARTITION} ar "
"${DEVICE}."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:22
msgid "Do you want to return to the partitioning menu?"
msgstr "A hoffech ddychwelyd i'r ddewislen rhaniadu?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:22
msgid ""
"No mount point is assigned for the ext2 (revision 0) file system in "
"partition #${PARTITION} of ${DEVICE}."
msgstr ""
"Does dim pwynt clymu wedi ei benodi ar system ffeiliau ext2 (diwygiad 0) yn "
"rhaniad #${PARTITION} ar ${DEVICE}."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:22
msgid ""
"If you do not go back to the partitioning menu and assign a mount point from "
"there, this partition will not be used at all."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych chi'n dychwelyd i'r ddewislen rhaniadu a'n dewis pwynt clymu "
"o'r fan hynny, ni chaiff y rhaniad hwn ei ddefnyddio o gwbl."

#. Type: select
#. Choices
#: ../templates:31
msgid "/, /boot, Enter manually, Do not mount it"
msgstr "/, /boot, Rhoi â llaw, Peidio a'i glymu"

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../templates:36
msgid "Mount point for this partition:"
msgstr "Pwynt clymu ar gyfer y rhaniad hwn:"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid "Invalid mount point"
msgstr "Pwynt clymu annilys"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid "The mount point you entered is invalid."
msgstr "Mae'r pwynt clymu a rhoddwyd yn annilys."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:40
msgid "Mount points must start with \"/\". They cannot contain spaces."
msgstr "Rhaid i bwyntiau clymu gychwyn efo \"/\". Ni chant gynnwys bylchau."

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "noatime - do not update inode access times at each access"
msgstr "noatime - peidio a diweddaru amser cyrchu inodau ar bob cyrchiad"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "nodev - do not support character or block special devices"
msgstr "nodev - peidio a chynal dyfeisiau arbennig nod neu floc"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "nosuid - ignore set-user-identifier or set-group-identifier bits"
msgstr ""
"nosuid - anwybyddu didau gosod-adnabyddyd-defnyddiwr neu gosod-adnabyddydd-"
"grŵp"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "noexec - do not allow execution of any binaries"
msgstr "noexec - peidio a chaniatau gweithredu rhaglenni"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "ro - mount the file system read-only"
msgstr "ro - clymu'r system ffeil fel un darllen-yn-unig"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "sync - all input/output activities occur synchronously"
msgstr "sync - mae pob gweithred mewnbwn/allbwn yn digwydd yn gydamserus"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "usrquota - user disk quota accounting enabled"
msgstr "usrquota - mae cyfrifo cwota disg defnyddiwr wedi ei alluogi"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Choices
#: ../templates:52
msgid "grpquota - group disk quota accounting enabled"
msgstr "grpquota - mae cyfrifo cwota disg grŵp wedi ei alluogi"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../templates:53
msgid "Mount options:"
msgstr "Opsiynnau clymu:"

#. Type: multiselect
#. Description
#: ../templates:53
msgid "Mount options can tune the behavior of the file system."
msgstr "Gall opsiynnau clymu addasu ymddygiad y system ffeiliau."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. File system name
#: ../templates:59
msgid "old Ext2 (revision 0) file system"
msgstr "hen system ffeiliau Ext2 (diwygiad 0)"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. Short file system name (untranslatable in many languages)
#: ../templates:64
msgid "ext2r0"
msgstr "ext2r0"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:68
msgid ""
"Your boot partition has not been configured with the old ext2 (revision 0) "
"file system.  This is needed by your machine in order to boot.  Please go "
"back and use the old ext2 (revision 0) file system."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw eich rhaniad bŵt wedi ei gyflunio gyda'r hen system ffeiliau ext2 "
"(diwygiad 0). Mae hyn yn angenrheidiol er mwyn i'ch beiriant fŵtio. Os "
"gwelwch yn dda, ewch yn ôl a defnyddiwch y system ffeiliau ext2 (diwygiad 0)."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:79
msgid ""
"Your boot partition is not located on the first primary partition of your "
"hard disk.  This is needed by your machine in order to boot.  Please go back "
"and use your first primary partition as a boot partition."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw eich rhanid bŵt wedi ei leoli ar rhaniad cynradd cyntaf eich disgen "
"galed. Mae hyn yn angenrheidiol er mwyn i'ch beiriant fŵtio. Os gwelwch yn "
"dda, ewch yn ôl a defnyddiwch eich rhaniad cynradd cyntaf fel rhaniad bŵtio."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:90
msgid "Go back to the menu and correct this problem?"
msgstr "Mynd yn ôl i'r ddewislen a chywiro'r broblem hwn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:90
msgid ""
"Your root partition is not a primary partition of your hard disk.  This is "
"needed by your machine in order to boot.  Please go back and use a primary "
"partition for your root partition."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw eich rhaniad gwraidd yn rhanid cynradd ar eich disgen galed. Mae hyn "
"yn angenrheidiol er mwyn i'ch beiriant fŵtio. Os gwelwch yn dda, ewch yn ôl "
"a defnyddiwch rhaniad cynradd ar gyfer eich rhaniad gwraidd."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../templates:90
msgid ""
"If you do not go back to the partitioning menu and correct this error, the "
"partition will be used as is.  This means that you may not be able to boot "
"from your hard disk."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych chi'n mynd yn ôl i'r ddewislen rhaniadu a chywiro'r gwall hwn, "
"caiff y rhaniad ei ddefnyddio fel y mae. Fe all hyn olygu nad ydych chi'n "
"gallu bŵtio o'ch disgen galed."
